channel.title: Where to powercut trees/oaks/willows!
channel.description:
If you are using a powercutter, I have found an AWESOME place to use it! It is North West of crafting guild, south of fally. No one ever goes there and there is tons of all F2P trees except for yews. Here's a pic of the place (I have put in dots on paint to represent the trees- look at the key at bottom of the image):
[img]http://www.fileden.com/files/2007/2/16/781396/where%20to%20power%20chop%20trees.bmp[/img]
Enjoy powercutting =]
-Harry
